{"tid":1360404,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再搞肥仔聰啦","createTime":"2019-07-24T10:43:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T14:51:28.000Z","uid":6826,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d9148253384d272975cdb90e8f83895b265ac6b0","tid":1360404,"uid":6826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:43:59.000Z","msg":"其實係咪唔應該再搞聰聰？<br />\n目標應該直指未來一哥<br />\n現任副處長 行動處處長<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鄧炳強</span></span><br />\n宜家既所有圍補行動 包括旺角沙田都係佢策劃<br />\n本身又係圍村人出生<br />\n元朗恐襲一定有份落order叫啲警察唔好理！<br />\n劉細良個網台節目都講過<br />\n呢條友極危險<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">俾呢條友做到一哥香港一定會仆街，未來一定更多元朗恐襲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n聰聰其實只係代罪羊 屌佢地係無用嫁啦！<br />\n一定要阻止到呢條友上台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fceb9bb3de62a61c54398aaf97cadcae2d87bb90","tid":1360404,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:47:25.000Z","msg":"唔好比鄧柄強上到位"},{"pid":"fc4c106f90bc8a832d888508c29ae6bab981e816","tid":1360404,"uid":6826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:53:56.000Z","msg":"呢條友一上台<br />\n局勢一定癲過宜家"},{"pid":"de58ce0222c338419b48aee4b848c584aba59257","tid":1360404,"uid":244309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:01:00.000Z","msg":"鄧X強 好明顯是對721恐襲 完全知情<br />\n機本上所有圍村人都知果日會做野"},{"pid":"438932260c5b17014b8e7d2d771ac4f570a72efe","tid":1360404,"uid":6826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de58ce0222c338419b48aee4b848c584aba59257","tid":1360404,"uid":244309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:01:00.000Z","msg":"鄧X強 好明顯是對721恐襲 完全知情<br />\n機本上所有圍村人都知果日會做野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:02:39.000Z","msg":"佢自己本身都係圍村人<br />\n同班元朗鄉民都好frd下"},{"pid":"27142809f234adef6b7b2b35ff8e8f728235d43d","tid":1360404,"uid":6826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco